Treatment outcome will be estimated at timepoint 12 months, additional timepoints for some parameters may be estimated at 3 and|or 6 months. The main outcome parameters are frequency and type of seizures, anxiety, depression, paroxysmal spike-wave EEG activity, NHS seizure severity score. Patient response to MSC-based cell therapy was estimated at 50% and 100% threshold in seizure frequency reduction.
